{"arkId":"cl010099346","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010099346","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Tabati\u00e8re rectangulaire","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Tabati\u00e8re rectangulaire"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Louis XV (1715-1774) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1757","currentLocation":"Sully, [OArt] Salle 614 - Galerie Louis XV, Vitrine 12","room":"Salle 614, Aile Aile Sully, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1757,"endYear":"","imprecision":"","text":"Milieu du XVIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Ducrollay, Jean-Charles","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"vers 1712","place":"","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"avant 1766","place":"Paris","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Orf\u00e8vre","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 6753","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"accessoire personnel, bo\u00eete, \u00e9tui","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Tabati\u00e8re d\u0027or rectangulaire au couvercle l\u00e9g\u00e8rement bomb\u00e9. Les six faces sont \u00e9maill\u00e9es en plein de six cartels \u00e0 bouquets de fleurs trait\u00e9es au naturel. Ceux-ci sont dispos\u00e9s sur des tablettes de pierre. Le tout sur un fond gris ombr\u00e9. Autour de chacun des cartels, un encadrement de crosses sym\u00e9triques en or cisel\u00e9, avec r\u00e9serves \u00e9maill\u00e9es en basse-taille de vert translucide sur fond quadrill\u00e9 \u00e0 petits fleurons. \r\nLa peinture sur \u00e9mail de bouquets de fleurs rappelle la mani\u00e8re de peindre de Philippe Parpette, peintre de fleurs \u00e0 la manufacture de porcelaine de S\u00e8vres \u00e0 partir de 1755.","inscriptions":"Poin\u00e7on : \r ; Coquille (1756 - 1762) (Poin\u00e7on de d\u00e9charge : sur la gorge)\r ; Herse (1756 - 1762) (Poin\u00e7on de charge : Dans le fond de la bo\u00eete, sur le revers du couvercle, sur le revers de la b\u00e2te)\r ; Lettre Q (1756 - 1757) (Poin\u00e7on de maison commune : Dans le fond de la bo\u00eete, sur le revers du couvercle, sur le revers de la b\u00e2te)\r ; Poin\u00e7on de ma\u00eetre orf\u00e8vre (Dans le fond de la bo\u00eete, sur le revers du couvercle, sur le revers de la b\u00e2te)","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"4","displayDimension":"4 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"8,2","displayDimension":"8,2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"6","displayDimension":"6 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : or\r\nTechnique : cisel\u00e9 = ciselure (techniques m\u00e9tal)\r\nTechnique : \u00e9mail peint (techniques m\u00e9tal-\u003E\u00e9maill\u00e9 = \u00e9maillage = \u00e9mail = \u00e9maux)","placeOfCreation":"Paris (France-\u003EIle-de-France = Ile de France)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Collection baron Basile de Schlichting (1857-1914) Paris. Legs 1914","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Baron Schlichting, Basile de","note":"","role":", Donateur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"legs","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date","value":"1914","startYear":1914,"endYear":1914}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moy